TAINED IN A BEHAVIOR RATING SCALE. CRIMINAL SUBJECTS RATED THE GROUP ENCOUNTER SESSIONS HIGHLY, WITH ATTENDANCE DATA DEMONSTRATING THEY PREFERRED A THERAPEUTIC EXPERIENCE OVER A HOBBY AND GAME EXPERIENCE. SUPPORTING DATA AND REFERENCES ARE PROVIDED. (DEP)
